ent/uploads/2021/12/993ffe98.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ScienceYTChannels_hero\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/993ffe98.png\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/993ffe98.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/104955/the-best-youtube-channels-for-science-enthusiasts/\" title=\"The 9 Best YouTube Channels for Science Enthusiasts\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tThe 9 Best YouTube Channels for Science Enthusiasts\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eDid you know? YouTube has tons of cool science channels that are equal parts education and entertainment. These are our faves!\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"the-best-content-creators-on-youtube-need-financial-support\"\u003e\n                        The Best Content Creators on YouTube Need Financial Support\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe thing is, making even very basic content for YouTube is expensive. When I started out \u003ca href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Online-Tech-Tips/videos\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emaking tech videos\u003c/a\u003e we had to invest in lights, a good camera with a decent lens, microphones, a teleprompter, and more. I had to dedicate a room in the house I rented for recording, and then there\u0026#39;s the labor of actually editing the video together and putting it out there, and the price of the software.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eUltimately, that channel let us make our money back, but without monetization it simply wouldn\u0026#39;t have been sustainable. Your favorite Youtuber probably has even more expensive costs in order to create better quality content. As the standard for YouTube content goes up, so does the cost of making that content.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eIf you want a given content creator that you love to keep making that content, they need some way to cover their costs. That money \u003cem\u003ehas\u003c/em\u003e to come from somewhere.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"youtube-is-expensive-to-run\"\u003e\n                        YouTube Is Expensive to Run\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                                                        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n\u003cp\u003eIt\u0026#39;s not just the content creators that need financial support to make the content, the platform provider has enormous expenditure as well. YouTube doesn\u0026#39;t run on magic; it consists of thousands of servers inside data centers that have to perform video conversions, and, of course, the actual streaming of content using massive amounts of bandwidth.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eObviously, YouTube is intended to be a for-profit business, but if no money comes in because of ad-blockers or a disinterest in paying for YouTube Premium, the service would fold virtually overnight. That\u0026#39;s not some fancy business analysis; it\u0026#39;s common sense.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"people-seem-to-object-to-paying-for-youtube-in-principle\"\u003e\n                        People Seem to Object to Paying for YouTube in Principle\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhich is why I\u0026#39;m so surprised to see a consistent attitude online that YouTube should be free, but that it should also have no advertising. My question is how that\u0026#39;s supposed to work? It\u0026#39;s almost as if people think of YouTube as a public service, but it\u0026#39;s not funded using taxpayer money.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eA primary complaint is that the level of advertising on YouTube has reached unwatchable levels. I don\u0026#39;t disagree with that at all, but you have to ask \u003cem\u003ewhy\u003c/em\u003e YouTube needs to push so many ads. It\u0026#39;s easy to assume that it\u0026#39;s just corporate greed at work, but if you think about it, heavy advertising is more an act of desperation than necessity. \u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"2ce4-4d9c-a59361109592\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/more-ads-are-coming-to-youtube-premium-lite/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"youtube premium logo in quotes.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/youtube-premium-quotes-logo.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMaking your customer experience worse is just as liable to decreasing your profits as people go elsewhere, but YouTube seems compelled to test our tolerance for ads, and that tells me they have no other choice. There\u0026#39;s probably a spiral of people circumventing advertising, leading to YouTube increasing ads, leading to more ad-blocking, etcetera, etcetera.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"3fae-43ef-b9190811ab45\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/youtube-is-in-an-arms-race-with-ad-blockers-and-ad-blockers-might-lose/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"YouTube logo and an ad block, with a nuclear bomb explosion between them.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/youtube-logo-and-an-ad-block-with-a-nuclear-bomb-explosion-between-them.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhenever someone mentions paying for YouTube Premium to be rid of ads, there\u0026#39;s a litany of replies vowing never to pay for YouTube. Even the cheaper YouTube Premium \u0026#34;Lite\u0026#34; with reduced ads for some money doesn\u0026#39;t seem to be swaying public opinion.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"if-you-want-youtube-to-stay-you-need-to-pay\"\u003e\n                        If You Want YouTube to Stay, You Need to Pay\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eMy question then is that, if you enjoy YouTube content or find it valuable in any way, wouldn\u0026#39;t you want it to stick around? The money to make it all work has to come from somewhere. That means advertising or subscription money. These days, many YouTube creators are forced to take sponsorships because ad revenue just isn\u0026#39;t good enough anymore. Something I see as a negative in some cases, because it has the potential to make them less independent and impartial. So it\u0026#39;s in your best interest to keep your content free from commercial influence.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eIf you want to keep enjoying YouTube content, you need to pay for it. If you feel it isn\u0026#39;t worth anything, then you have no reason to consume it. You can pay with your time (i.e. watching an advert) or you can pay in cash. These days, you can even give cash to a specific YouTube channel without pushing that money into the general pool shared among all monetized channels.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"871f-4c11-932e8ae67585\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/how-to-use-youtube-premium-as-a-productivity-app/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A man working on his laptop, the YouTube Premium logo in the background and some YouTube icons around.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yt-premium.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003chr/\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere\u0026#39;s this strange situation where the same people who will happily pay to have an ad-free experience on services like Netflix or Hulu, won\u0026#39;t do the same thing on YouTube, even though \u003cem\u003emost\u003c/em\u003e of their streaming time is spent watching YouTube content. What worries me is that if things keep going the way they are, there won\u0026#39;t \u003cem\u003ebe\u003c/em\u003e any YouTube content to watch.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
